@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mywtlq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.05 - v2 + 0.10)) / (0.05 * tmp))
    v1 = wp.abs((0.70 / wp.sin(v2 + 0.40)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp((v2 + 0.32 - tmp + 0.26)))
    v1 = (0.54 + ((tmp + 0.34 * v0 + 0.16) - v1))
    data[tid] = v0
